<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Redirect Control - Home</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('../partials/header', { user, active: 'home' }) %>
    <div class="container-xxl">
        <section class="page-intro mb-4">
            <div class="row align-items-center g-4">
                <div class="col-lg-7">
                    <div class="feature-badge mb-3">Chao mung, <%= user.username %></div>
                    <p class="eyebrow mb-2">Trung tam he thong</p>
                    <h1 class="mb-3">Redirect chi la mot module. Day la hub dieu khien toan bo he thong.</h1>
                    <p class="text-muted mb-4">Su dung menu "Chuc nang" de vao tung khu vuc: Redirect, he thong hoat dong va quan tri nguoi dung. Cac phan khac se duoc bo sung dan trong roadmap.</p>
                    <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/redirect"><i class="fa-solid fa-bolt me-2"></i>Mo Redirect</a>
                        <% if (user.role_name === 'super_admin') { %>
                            <a class="btn btn-outline-dark" href="/admin/system"><i class="fa-solid fa-server me-2"></i>Trang he thong</a>
                        <% } %>
                        <% if (user.role_name === 'super_admin' || user.role_name === 'admin') { %>
                            <a class="btn btn-outline-dark" href="/users"><i class="fa-solid fa-users-gear me-2"></i>Quan tri nguoi dung</a>
                        <% } %>
                    </div>
                    <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-3 mt-3">
                        <span class="badge bg-light text-dark border border-0">Role: <%= user.role_name %></span>
                        <span class="badge bg-light text-dark border border-0">Ho tro: @mvp2025</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-5">
                    <div class="card-surface h-100">
                        <div class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-between mb-3">
                            <h5 class="fw-bold mb-0">Ban do chuc nang</h5>
                            <span class="text-muted small">Trang chu</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="action-grid">
                            <div class="action-card">
                                <div class="label">Redirect</div>
                                <h5 class="mb-2">Quan ly domain & link</h5>
                                <p class="text-muted mb-3">Them/sua domain, link redirect, xem thong ke luu luong.</p>
                                <a class="btn btn-sm btn-primary" href="/redirect">Mo Redirect</a>
                            </div>
                            <% if (user.role_name === 'super_admin') { %>
                                <div class="action-card">
                                    <div class="label">He thong</div>
                                    <h5 class="mb-2">Trang thai hoat dong</h5>
                                    <p class="text-muted mb-3">Kiem tra uptime, tai nguyen server va ket noi database.</p>
                                    <a class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-dark" href="/admin/system">Xem he thong</a>
                                </div>
                            <% } %>
                            <% if (user.role_name === 'super_admin' || user.role_name === 'admin') { %>
                                <div class="action-card">
                                    <div class="label">Nguoi dung</div>
                                    <h5 class="mb-2">Phan quyen & quan tri</h5>
                                    <p class="text-muted mb-3">Quan ly tai khoan, role va phan quyen truy cap.</p>
                                    <a class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-dark" href="/users">Quan tri</a>
                                </div>
                            <% } %>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-3">
            <div class="row g-3">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="card-surface h-100">
                        <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-2">
                            <h6 class="fw-bold mb-0">Huong phat trien</h6>
                            <span class="badge bg-light text-dark border border-0">Soon</span>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-muted mb-3">Cac module bo sung (giay to, bao cao nang cao, cau hinh he thong) se duoc dua vao menu "Chuc nang" khi san sang.</p>
                        <ul class="text-muted small mb-0">
                            <li>Tap trung vao trang chu de dan duong ro rang.</li>
                            <li>Giu main content chieu cao day du de footer nam cuoi trang.</li>
                            <li>Bo sung menu tong hop de nguoi dung di chuyen nhanh.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="card-surface h-100">
                        <h6 class="fw-bold mb-2">Cap nhat gan day</h6>
                        <div class="text-muted small">
                            <p class="mb-2">- Header moi gom logo/text, menu chuc nang va khu vuc tai khoan.</p>
                            <p class="mb-2">- Trang chu tao diem neo de trinh bay toan bo he thong.</p>
                            <p class="mb-0">- Footer giu thong tin @mvp2025, main phu hop ke ca khi noi dung it.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>
    <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
